    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
      <head>Scope and Content
</head>
      <p>Will books, 1749-1791, of Culpeper County Court.  The will books include the name oftestator, list of heirs, and year the wills were proven in court.  They also include probate records such as inventories and appraisements.  Will Book B does not have an index.
</p>
    </scopecontent>
